Package: daltonist
Type: Package
Title: Colorblindness Accessibility Tools 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: William K. Petry [aut, cre] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0002-5230-5987>>)
Maintainer: William K. Petry <william.petry@usys.ethz.ch>
Description: Provides tools for the colorblind to identify colors and for the
    non-colorblind to ensure accessibility of color palettes.
URL: https://github.com/wpetry/daltonist
BugReports: https://github.com/wpetry/daltonist/issues
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 3.3.0)
Imports: colorspace (>= 1.4-0), colorscience (>= 1.0.4), httr (>= 1.3.1), jsonlite (>= 1.5)
Suggests: colorblindr, ggplot2 (>= 2.2.1.900), dplyr (>= 0.7-0), tidyr (>= 0.7-2),
    tibble (>= 1.4.1), pracma
